array.string: An award-winning Korean Food option, the Sorabol Korean Restaurant is conveniently located across the street from Walmart on Keeaumoku St, and provides diners a truly exceptional menu filled with delicious Korean favorites. They are opened every day all day, and are a very popular spot for those winding down a night of revelry.
